                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is the countryside a good place to raise children?
It has two sides 
(+) ->  On the positive side, the countryside has good environment it is good for their health. They have more friends, more space for playing outside. They can play sports together.
(-) -> On the negative side, it lacks of facilities to develop. In the country less schools, hospital, libraries, ...  
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-27.1)</h3><p><div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 flex items-center gap-4">
