                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How do you celebrate birthdays?
-> To celebrate brithdays, i often gather with friends and families to have small party. We will eat cakes, drink sodies and talk overngiht.A wonderful experience ! 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-27.2)</h3><p><div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 flex items-center gap-4">
