                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is a traditional festival in your country?
-> Tet is one of the most famous traditional festival in Viet Nam. It is held in february every years. Tet is feelings. Every year i come back my hometown and prepare for Tet (buy lantern, flowers, .. to decorate my house). Make dishes to share in the count down night. I wish i have more time for my family. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-27.3)</h3><p><div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 flex items-center gap-4">
