+) at first, i felt nervous, before the interview, i prepared carefully and have a good look. During the interview, i focus only on the questions from the interviewer. At the end, i passed. I feel happy, i think that confidence is the key.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-32.2)</h3><p><div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 flex items-center gap-4">
