                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> 1. Confidence (tự tin). -> confidence is the key  
2.good preparation -> Good documents, practise some questions and try to answer it.
3. Remember to have a good look -> Looks tell a lot about a us. Wearing formal (proper) clothes is a way to respect the partner. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-32.3)</h3><p><div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 flex items-center gap-4">
