                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Yes, of course, the cadidate should wear formal clothes when attending the interview. Looks tell a lot about us. It is a way to respect the intervewer. It helps the recruiter to evaluate you well. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-33.1)</h3><p><div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 flex items-center gap-4">
