                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> In the next 5 years, i will be a leader in departure and manage more staffs. have a job with higher salary, more benefits, ... I want to travel to more places to explore the world. or i will open my flower shop or coffee shop </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-33.3)</h3><p><div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 flex items-center gap-4">
